originalText.text: Rosemarie is a truly gifted healer. She's incredibly intuitive, tapped in and knows exactly what you need without you needing to explain. What she does is really special and cannot really be articulated, but the positive effects I've felt on my energy and mental & emotional state have been nothing short of amazing!

originalText.text: Rosemarie Fem is a gifted and powerful Reiki healer. I’ve been lucky enough to do several sessions with her and I always get the impression like she goes to work and gets things done. I feel things have been lifted and cleared and unblocked. She’s professional and is excellent with boundaries and it’s important that your healer themselves are in a good place and Rosemarie is very composed, energetic, heart connected and aligned herself. Thanks Rosemarie!

originalText.text: Rosemarie was able to align three of my chakras in a matter of one hour. I felt the realignment and was clear of mind for a few days afterward. Rosemarie made me feel quite comfortable during the experience as well even through a zoom call! She was able to accommodate to my busy schedule as well. I can’t recommend this lovely soul and human enough!
